               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200412-109-cd623" type="crimeDate">6th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200412-109-off622 t18200412-109-cd623"></join>, two handkerchiefs, value 7 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18200412-109-victim1010" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Sowerby
                  <interp inst="t18200412-109-victim1010" type="surname" value="Sowerby"></interp>
